暴動、性罪行等，學校應暫停有關教職員職務，即使有關教職員未被控以任何罪名，學校亦應詳細檢視事件性質。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄強調，無論被捕教師是否被定罪，當局都會在法律程序完結後，檢視有關教師註冊的資格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582291-20210324.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582291-20210324.htm&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2KnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=e18b96ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1582291-20210324.htm&h=22cedd04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1582291-20210324.htm</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"周浩L支持未審先判，支持中共特色社會人治主義法制"},{"pid":"7ca3684988f1f7d4b205c0cf375568f51fd7f4db","tid":2459293,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91993b6615a541016c66947a0836886e0bec3e36","tid":2459293,"uid":4826,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"做教師都幾辛苦，五方受敵<br />\n<br />\n東：家長<br />\n南：學生<br />\n西：老細<br />\n北：政府<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中：連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"文革2.0 批鬥哂啲知識份子"},{"pid":"47d0e7735b37095d594dc3c72b67324fa658ee03","tid":2459293,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:43:20.000Z","msg":"仔女去曬澳洲<br />\n叫人地仔女愛國<br />\n楊潤雄死全家啦"},{"pid":"62bc514235cb124796a77964204ff3a9f9cadfd1","tid":2459293,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"條罪叫 參與暴動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f23ed54477bad85d6a38f04856797a88a9402af","tid":2459293,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T05:46:17.000Z","msg":"繼續文革，停唔到"},{"pid":"3831b38e03807e3afeb418ed9492a2d62ffe2119","tid":2459293,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"